                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6184" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">SCLM-0144</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9114 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">打造弹性供应链：比亚迪的“芯”布局</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Build a Flexible Supply Chain: BYD&#39;s &quot;Chip&quot; Layout</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">魏旭光，张星，韩天琦，李向东</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">河北工业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">比亚迪股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">电子工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采购供应部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">12 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">供应链风险管理；“芯”布局；弹性供应链；供应链重构</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Supply chain risk management; &quot; chip&quot; layout; Resilient supply chain; Supply chain restructuring</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">新冠肺炎疫情引起的芯片短缺正在严重冲击全球汽车制造业，以丰田、大众、福特为代表的国际领先车企受到重创。与之形成对比的是，比亚迪于4月7日表示，由于提前布局车载芯片的研发、制造，目前全球汽车行业经历的缺芯停产问题，比亚迪没有受到影响。自2003年成立第六事业部开始，比亚迪在芯片研发的进程中，经历了“禁售”打压、市场对国产芯片的质疑，已经成长为拥有涉及芯片设计、晶圆制造、封装测试和下游应用的完整供应链的独立车企。本案例以新冠肺炎疫情引发的汽车制造业芯片荒为背景，着眼于比亚迪芯片供应链风险识别与应对策略。旨在引发学生思考供应链风险以及企业如何通过弹性布局和重构，打造自主可控、安全高效的供应链。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">The shortage of chips caused by the COVID-19 is severely hitting the global automobile manufacturing industry, and leading international auto companies represented by Toyota, Volkswagen, and Ford have been hit hard. In contrast, BYD stated on April 7 that BYD has not been influenced by the current shortage of chip production and shutdown problems experienced by the global automotive industry due to the advancement of the development and manufacturing of on-board chips. Since the establishment of the Sixth Division in 2003, BYD has experienced the &quot;ban on sales&quot; and the market’s questioning of domestic chips in the process of chip research and development, BYD has grown into an independent car company with a complete supply chain involving chip design, wafer manufacturing, packaging and testing, and downstream applications. The case is based on the chip shortage of the automobile manufacturing industry caused by the COVID-19, and focuses on the risk identification and response strategy of BYD&#39;s chip supply chain. It aims to induce students to think about supply chain risks and how companies can create an autonomous, controllable, safe and efficient supply chain through flexible layout and restructuring.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《供应链管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“供应链风险管理”</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-03</td>
                            </tr>
